    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Get ready for a dependable ride with this honest daily driver! This vehicle has been a faithful companion and, while it shows some natural wear and tear from its years on the road, it still runs well and is ready for many more miles. It's a practical, budget-friendly choice for anyone looking for a solid car that gets the job done with a bit of character!",
